Business Brief -- Yamaichi Securities Co.:
   Two Offices Will Be Shut
   Due to Weak Stock Market
Yamaichi also announced a regular, twice-a-year relocation
program involving 778 employees.
   A Yamaichi spokesman said both of the offices being closed
were generating relatively slim margins. Yamaichi will
consolidate operations of the offices into nearby branches.
   Yamaichi was the only one of Japan's Big Four brokerage
houses to report a loss for the fiscal first half ended Sept.
30.